== 風險 ==

2010年2月，来自剑桥大学的研究人员发现EMV协议的一个重大安全漏洞，使得攻击者能够对芯片+密码模式的IC卡发起中间人攻击，绕过IC卡的脱机密码校验，无论在终端机上输入何种密码，都能够使用IC卡。<ref>{{cite web|author1=Flow Yu|title=劍橋大學學生發現晶片卡交易機制的漏洞|url=https://chinese.engadget.com/2010/02/18/cambridge-university-finds-credit-card-security-flaw-uses-the-m/|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]中文版|accessdate=2018-01-26|date=2010-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124135753/https://chinese.engadget.com/2010/02/18/cambridge-university-finds-credit-card-security-flaw-uses-the-m/|archive-date=2018-01-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cambridge Study: EMV Secure? Nope.|url=https://www.pymnts.com/in-depth/2014/cambridge-study-emv-secure-nonce-sense/|website=PYMNTS|accessdate=2018-01-26|date=2014-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125184131/https://www.pymnts.com/in-depth/2014/cambridge-study-emv-secure-nonce-sense/|archive-date=2019-01-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://wired.gq.com.tw/posts/pinpadpwned |title=英美常用信用卡終端機遭揭有重大漏洞 |date=2012-08-20 |accessdate=2014-10-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20141021071051/http://wired.gq.com.tw/posts/pinpadpwned |archivedate=2014-10-21 }}</ref><ref>[http://steventalk.wordpress.com/2010/02/21/ic-cards-are-vulnerable-to-mitm-attacks/ IC cards are vulnerable to MITM attacks]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

